articles.author: MSNBC.com
articles.title: Sen. Brian Schatz on whether we can trust Trump to handle coronavirus
articles.description: Sen. Brian Schatz (D-HI): “To the extent we’ve been fortunate with this disease is because of its epidemiology, not because of some sort of coordinated response from the government.”

articles.author: MSNBC.com
articles.title: How Trump handled the last global health crisis
articles.description: Can we trust Trump to handle coronavirus? His response to the Ebola outbreak in 2014—and his recent comments—don't offer much reason for optimism.
